-- Listage des données de la table playranker.post : ~31 rows (environ)
INSERT INTO `post` (`id`, `topic_id`, `user_id`, `content`, `created_at`) VALUES
	(103, 76, 15, 'What are your favorite mobile games this year? I’m really enjoying Marvel Snap for its fast strategy and Honkai: Star Rail for its immersive world. What are you playing these days?ouez à quoi en ce moment ?', '2024-10-08 07:10:47'),
	(104, 77, 15, 'The latest Clash Royale update changed a lot of deck dynamics. Do you have any tips on new strategies to adopt?', '2024-10-08 07:11:08'),
	(105, 78, 15, 'For me, Mario Kart 8 Deluxe on the Switch is unbeatable, especially with the new DLC featuring classic tracks. But I also remember spending hours on Mario Kart Wii. What\'s your favorite?', '2024-10-08 07:11:19'),
	(106, 79, 15, 'I play a lot of Super Smash Bros. Ultimate, and my mains are Link and Inkling. Who are your go-to characters? Any tips for improving in competitive mode?', '2024-10-08 07:11:33'),
	(107, 80, 15, 'Baldur\'s Gate 3 has got me hooked on tactical RPGs. I mainly play as a druid for the animal transformations. What\'s your favorite class?', '2024-10-08 07:13:35'),
	(108, 81, 15, 'In Starfield, I spend more time exploring planets than following the main quests. What\'s your approach to the game?', '2024-10-08 07:13:46'),
	(109, 82, 15, 'I just finished God of War: Ragnarök, and the story was incredible. What did you think of Kratos and Atreus\' relationship?', '2024-10-08 07:14:03'),
	(110, 83, 15, 'I just finished Marvel\'s Spider-Man 2 on PS5, and the combat is smoother than ever! The graphics are mind-blowing. How did you find the game?', '2024-10-08 07:14:16'),
	(111, 84, 15, 'I\'m torn between Super Metroid and The Legend of Zelda: A Link to the Past. What do you think is the best retro game on Super Nintendo?', '2024-10-08 07:14:33'),
	(112, 85, 15, 'If you were introducing someone to retro games, what would be your top 5 must-play titles? For me, it would include Sonic the Hedgehog, Street Fighter II, and Super Mario Bros..', '2024-10-08 07:14:46'),
	(113, 86, 15, 'Both are amazing, but which one do you prefer? Starfield for its space exploration or Forza Horizon 5 for its graphics and racing freedom?', '2024-10-08 07:15:17'),
	(114, 87, 15, 'I think Halo Infinite\'s campaign is very well done, but the multiplayer is just as fun. Do you spend more time in solo or multiplayer?', '2024-10-08 07:15:27'),
	(115, 77, 19, 'Definitely! I\'ve been experimenting with Miner Poison decks, and they’ve been working wonders with the new balance changes. Also, don’t sleep on the Mega Minion—it’s a great value card right now.', '2024-10-08 07:19:30'),
	(116, 76, 19, 'I’ve been hooked on Apex Legends Mobile recently. The controls are surprisingly smooth, and it feels just like the console version. I also play Among Us with friends when we want something light and fun.', '2024-10-08 07:19:52'),
	(117, 78, 20, 'I totally agree! Mario Kart 8 Deluxe is the best overall experience, but I have a soft spot for Mario Kart DS because of the mission mode. It added something different that I miss in newer titles.', '2024-10-08 07:20:38'),
	(118, 79, 20, 'I main Zero Suit Samus and Roy. As for tips, try to master short hopping and learn how to space your moves properly. It’ll make a big difference, especially against faster characters.', '2024-10-08 07:20:48'),
	(119, 80, 19, 'I\'m loving the wizard class for all the spell combinations and versatility. Casting fireball never gets old! Druids are great too though—wild shape opens up a lot of fun possibilities.', '2024-10-08 07:21:24'),
	(120, 81, 19, 'Same here! I’m always curious about what I’ll find next. Sometimes I just wander around collecting resources and scanning wildlife. I think I’ve only completed like 3 main missions so far!', '2024-10-08 07:21:33'),
	(121, 82, 21, '"I loved their dynamic too! The tension between them felt real, and it was interesting to see Atreus mature and grow. I think the game nailed the father-son relationship in a way that’s rare in gaming.', '2024-10-08 07:22:25'),
	(122, 83, 21, 'Completely agree! I thought the story was amazing too, especially the twists with the villains. The new gadgets and abilities also make swinging through the city even more fun!', '2024-10-08 07:22:36'),
	(123, 84, 20, 'ough choice! For me, it’s A Link to the Past. It defined so many of the series’ staples and still holds up today. Super Metroid is a masterpiece too though, especially for the atmosphere.', '2024-10-08 07:23:26'),
	(124, 85, 20, 'Great list! I’d add Castlevania: Symphony of the Night and Mega Man X to the mix. Those are classics that anyone interested in retro gaming should experience at least once.', '2024-10-08 07:23:37'),
	(125, 86, 22, 'I’m more into Forza Horizon 5. The open-world racing is so immersive, and I love the freedom to just drive around and explore. But I can see why Starfield has such a strong following too!', '2024-10-08 07:24:19'),
	(126, 87, 22, 'Definitely multiplayer for me. There’s something about Halo that just feels right in multiplayer. I like the campaign, but nothing beats the classic Slayer matches with friends.', '2024-10-08 07:24:26'),
	(127, 88, 22, 'There’s been a lot of debate about The Last of Us Part II. Personally, I think it’s a masterpiece with an incredible story, but I understand why some people feel differently. What’s your take on the game?', '2024-10-08 07:25:18'),
	(128, 89, 22, 'Now that Cyberpunk 2077 has received multiple patches and updates, I’m wondering if it’s finally worth diving into. Is the experience smoother now? How’s the gameplay and story holding up?', '2024-10-08 07:25:48'),
	(129, 88, 21, 'I’m in the same boat as you! The story was bold and took risks that paid off for me, especially with how it handled its characters. It’s not an easy game to digest, but that’s what makes it memorable. I can see why some people were upset though, the game does challenge expectations', '2024-10-08 07:26:34'),
	(130, 89, 21, 'Definitely worth playing now! The latest updates have made a huge difference, especially with stability and performance. The story was always strong, but now it’s backed up by smoother gameplay. I’d say give it a shot if you were waiting for the game to be fixed!', '2024-10-08 07:26:50'),
	(131, 90, 20, 'I’ve been a huge fan of Horizon Zero Dawn, but I’m wondering if Forbidden West really improves on the original. Is it worth picking up if you loved the first game?', '2024-10-08 07:29:31'),
	(132, 90, 19, 'I think it’s a solid improvement. The combat feels more refined, and the world is even more stunning. The story is great too, but it can feel overwhelming with so many side quests. If you loved Zero Dawn, I think you’ll enjoy this one.', '2024-10-08 07:32:17'),
	(133, 91, 19, 'With the release of Counter-Strike 2, there’s been a lot of excitement. I’ve been playing CS\r\nfor years—should I switch to the new one, or is it more of the same?', '2024-10-08 07:32:42');

